Implemented the command-tool unification.

`AgentToolExecutor.execute()` now handles the `command` domain, and `MCPToolController` no longer calls `CommandToolExecutor` directly for `command_run` / `command_status` / `command_result`. Instead, it resolves the agent from `commandService.session`, registers `commandService` as the `command` target, and dispatches through `agent.toolExtractor.execute(toolCall)`. I also updated the focused agentic and REST unit tests to cover that path.

The daily memory file at `coworker\tasks\300logs\2026\04\09\MEMORY.20260409.md` has been appended with this task’s summary and lessons. The monthly memory already contained the 2026-04-08 rollup, so no monthly reconciliation update was needed.


